# Beatrice — an artfully crafted intellect

![essence of Beatrice](beatrice.png)

**what —** Divine love and grace; the guide through Paradise.

**why —** Love that moves the sun and the other stars, reaching down to save him.

**how —** She sends Virgil first, then leads where Virgil cannot.

**where —** The Empyrean — the white rose of the blessed.

